-- Northern Ireland Police Say Pipe Bomb Found in North Belfast
-- B y   C o l m   H e a t l e y
-- 2013-01-31T09:27:18Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-01-31/northern-ireland-police-say-pipe-bomb-found-in-north-belfast.html
Northern Ireland police say they
found a bomb after investigating reports that a device had been
thrown at a police patrol in north Belfast late yesterday.  A pipe bomb was found in searches in the Old Park area and
has been taken away for further examination, a police spokesman
said in a recorded message. The area has been closed-off, the
unidentified spokesman said, without giving any further
information.  To contact the reporter on this story:
